thread.title: Quincy

author: Quincy
title: Quincy
text: A friend recommended Munchery, highly. I have only been a member a short time, having received just three cooked meals. Each was excellent. The pricing seems fair, the meal choices available are diverse and the delivery service was prompt, correct as to specified time with courteous, smiling delivery people. I am looking forward to future meals and wouldn't hesitate to recommend Munchery to friends.
